node.text: @tandeminlove wow! Old folks said it’s better to lose it later. 👍🏻

Zahn dropped his second tooth! He didn’t get anything from the tooth 🧚‍♀️ last time because he lost his 🦷! 🤦🏻‍♀️ So this time he ensured that he kept it properly after brushing it (thanks to reading Peppa Pig books). 😊 In fact, I had totally forgotten about it. And that was why in the vid, I wasn’t able to answer why there was nothing under his pillow when he woke up and tooth fairy only turned up afterwards! 😝 Please pardon my irritating high-pitch voice in the vid too.
@nanraj48 that’s why I had to “act” too! 😂
@mizprissy haha yes this is for his 2nd tooth. 😊
Haha wasn’t there a one dollar coin in his hand? We also dropped 2 already!
@danceyedna ❤️ thank you. Still can 骗! My older boys kept telling him tooth fairy is fake! 😅
@pocketpigdiary yes so long and thick! Everyday scream abt the 🥵
So funny ! And his hair is long 😆
@deedeedee13 yes 😂 she must be very busy! That’s why I told Zahn she works OT and came late.
Wow! Haha the Tooth Fairy has been collecting many teeth this CB. 2 from my kid too 🤣
My son lost 1 tooth as well during CB. His first tooth fell earlier this year and we gave him $5. The second tooth thistime round only $2 and he said “Tooth fairy no money during Covid?” LOL!!😂
@tandeminlove wow! Old folks said it’s better to lose it later. 👍🏻
yay! olive still has no loose teeth! 🙊
